{"tid":2515641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科興谷唔起 林鄭：醫護抹黑  員工陣線稱引科學數據講真相","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T09:37:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aa65ce422a3e78125d73eb6ed399ac17f7cebdcf","tid":2515641,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210504/M6ZZOJPHGBHN7C3MCVTX2F2NNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210504%2FM6ZZOJPHGBHN7C3MCVTX2F2NNY%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=0aa54526\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210504%2FM6ZZOJPHGBHN7C3MCVTX2F2NNY%2F&h=cb25cbed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210504/M6ZZOJPHGBHN7C3MCVTX2F2NNY/</a><br />\n<br />\n科興谷唔起 林鄭：醫護抹黑 <br />\n員工陣線稱引科學數據講真相<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府近日全力「谷針」，惟昨日網上預約接種疫苗數目未見大幅回升，特首林鄭月娥昨日出席醫院管理局研討大會時，將市民冷待疫苗歸咎於部份本港醫護人員將防疫措施政治化、抹黑國產疫苗並向公眾散播假消息，她又透露港府本月將向立法會提交引入海外醫生條例草案，為引入海外醫生鋪路。醫管局員工陣線反駁指工會僅分享科學實證，聲言會繼續堅守位置發聲。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：除口罩致辭 口沫橫飛10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n即使港府出動「旅遊氣泡」及「疫苗氣泡」谷針，但預約接種疫苗數字未見大幅上升，由本月1日有32,700人預約的高位跌至昨日只有21,600人預約，其中昨日科興預約數字更比復必泰少13,000人，僅4,300人預約接種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WovligDgwOGcPzbv0O1tPaf1ss4=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DZQR7NEYGZCLVO67VGVLMAZWL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWovligDgwOGcPzbv0O1tPaf1ss4%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDZQR7NEYGZCLVO67VGVLMAZWL4.jpg&h=60205dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■科興疫苗供港逾兩個月，接種率一直未如理想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅卓堯：以防疫打壓 市民失信心<br />\n<br />\n醫管局研討大會一連兩日於會展舉行，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：護航撐國貨 專家實打復必泰<br />\n<br />\n她又把抗疫成果與社會。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n面對林鄭批評，醫管局員工陣線副主席羅卓堯重申，工會僅引用外國科學數據道出科興疫苗的保護率較低，「我哋希望可以堅守住位置講真相出嚟」，反指林鄭以防疫為名，達致政治目的為實，硬推不同措施。他指市民不願接種疫苗，並非因所謂的醫護「抹黑」，而是政府過份硬推，並多次以防疫為由打壓，市民因此對政府缺乏信心，「就算想打針都唔想畀政府邀功，推高打針數字」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藉機力銷引入海外醫生條例草案<br />\n<br />\n林鄭不滿部份本港醫護人員未有配合谷針，推出具爭議性的引入海外醫生條例草案，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局主席范鴻齡表示，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n開幕禮上亦播放了。。。。。"},{"pid":"9655ef0c15b5420a5bf9c89aa8d9dd495ed4d448","tid":2515641,"uid":297152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"柒婆唔識講人話<br />\n不惜逼走利君雅"},{"pid":"384fb538e1b0c9ea69453a0a50fdc3b609107441","tid":2515641,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"&quot;特區政府的決策均以科學和理論為本&quot;<br />\n呢句乜水噏？定習慣鳩噏唔記得？"},{"pid":"a0a4b0ba8c5ed7fae5b215754d9c1b15a413ad71","tid":2515641,"uid":25107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"四萬個應該大部分都係被逼去打既工人姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf4c49775e70ee5391749f8dcd2628accf7c01f","tid":2515641,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"次次講親大話就話人抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67488dc9feabf0c7388c427bce99d631d7350539","tid":2515641,"uid":137038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"唔合心意嘅數據 = 唔科學、抹黑"},{"pid":"43a1f72f01563a9a80e8dc8374421be2bcd34abd","tid":2515641,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:28:54.000Z","msg":"限聚令已經自爆唔係科學理據"},{"pid":"21b9ab51f902bcde18bba7646d3601ddbe413829","tid":2515641,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:32:45.000Z","msg":"高價賣去印度咪得<br />\n幫補吓庫房都好丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38ecb42e62411c583949e241935be6cce9bc994","tid":2515641,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"為嗰班講真話嘅醫護擔心"},{"pid":"929408af550ee05789feecc28ad09fa039407555","tid":2515641,"uid":90742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"睇數據ok. <br />\n<br />\n第三期數據呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5391627879b98de9e54d960d5c821a6055c709b3","tid":2515641,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"原來科學數據唔啱林鄭心意就係抹黑"},{"pid":"7e54c1111f661d4d8799e9b70439095b59671a77","tid":2515641,"uid":28628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"G持強制性要公墓猿打4hing谷數"}]}